<p>The following is a table of improvisational games that I have used in the context of education, either as a student or a teacher. One of my goals for the <b>end of september</b> is to have authentification for users on the site, so you can leave suggestions for games you think would be at home in the list.</p>
              <table id="example" class="display" width="100%"></table>
